@miami.pro UNIVERSE CHAMPIONSHIP NOV 19TH 2023
 at @shawtheatreldn .

Due to serious complications with the original venue we had to find a new venue: @shawtheatreldn 100-110 Euston road, London NW1 2AJ .

Get ready for another huge Miami Pro Universe Fitness Model & Physique championships on NOV 19th 2023 at the brand new theatre in central London @shawtheatreldn,  Euston London.

This event will be hosted by top Fitness Model champion, published model & fitness writer @charliegarforth owner of @pro.physiques prep coaching. 

There's a massive 50 PRO CARDS TO BE AWARDED.
All top 3 winners in each category will win a Pro card & Pro status and get to compete in the PRO SHOW that day against the other pros, full schedule of category list coming next week. 

AMAZING PRIZES!
COMPETE AT ARNOLD'S UK 2024! 

That’s right, win to compete at the famous Arnolds Amateur UK Bodybuilding competition next year March 13th-14th 2024.

This prize will be awarded to the winner in the PRO SHOW to the Men’s Physique and Bikini winner. 
Yes your entry & stage photos will be paid for by Miami Pro, because we care about your bodybuilding career & future we want to help you kick-start your career the best way, and there’s no other better way than to compete on the prestigious stage of the Arnold’s UK Bodybuilding competition 2024.
...and more prizes to be added!

PLEASE NOTE:
*Miami Pro isn't affiliated with any other federation, we are a Fitness Model & Physique competition helping athletes to showcase their physique & talent on our stage. Miami Pro simply sponsor athletes to compete with IFBB shows. For more info on IFBB rules & regulations you must visit their website.
You must have done a regional show and be a membership to  the IFBB to compete *

SPECTATOR TICKETS: £25 buy from venue @shawtheatreldn or on show day at venue only.

•Nearest train station:Euston st.
•Nearest car park: NCP Euston Station 
•Athletes Registration: 
10.30am –11.30am at venue
•Athletes Meeting: 12pm-12:30pm sharp in venue arena.
•Doors open to public: 12.30pm

See y'all there!
